summary:

  • Post-sale holdings: 819,051 shares (direct and indirect) vs. 953,051 previously.
  • No closed period breach: Transactions did not violate trading policy.

No material capital markets impact identified (routine director share sale).

No material information identified (Annual Shareholders' Meeting notice - routine governance matters only).

- Record date for voting: 19 August 2025
- Meeting date: 21 August 2025

No financial, operational, or capital structure impacts disclosed.

No material information identified.
